                    <p>Role-based user system with secure authentication and authorization for different user types.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="bi bi-chat-dots"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Chat Support</h3>
                    <p>Real-time chat system with bot assistance and human agent support for customer inquiries.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Secure Platform</h3>
                    <p>Enterprise-grade security with encrypted data storage and secure user authentication.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
            <p>Join thousands of users who trust Luxprop Technology for their real estate management needs.</p>
            <div class="cta-actions">
                <a href="/user/create" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Create Account</a>
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">Sign In</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

